import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './layouts/App.vue'

Vue.config.productionTip = false

import './assets/css/base.css';//~~src
import './assets/js/font.js';//字体比值控制

//引入路由配置
import router from './plugins/router.js'

new Vue({
  render: h => h(App),
  router
}).$mount('#app')
